---
title: Chicken Breasts Chow Mein-Style Noodles with Stir-Fried Veggies and Peanuts
description: This stir-fry offers a perfect balance of flavours and textures. Savoury with a touch of sweetness, this dish combines tender-crisp veggies with irresistibly slurp-able noodles! A final sprinkle of crunchy peanuts gives this dinner 10s across the board!
